        "client_msg_id": "402bba2c-eb1e-4759-8928-d575c7c15a0b",
        "text": "Hi all :wave: , I’ve been wanting to say this for a while: I want to thank the C book club from last year. Even though I was only able to attend a few of the sessions, what I learned there was incredibly valuable and went far beyond the world of R: it carried over into my university classroom, where I now teach the course “Programming Paradigms in C” to computer science students. Despite my limited attendance at the sessions, I always felt supported and welcome, and it was a truly wonderful experience. That mutual influence between this community and my teaching practice is something for which I am truly grateful. :purple_heart: p\/d: Special thanks to <@U035M81N341> and <@U01DZUA88S1> for organizing the book club",
